\markup {
  \column 
  {
   \vspace #2
   \line { \large { I'm impressed with my attorney Bernie. I'm impressed with his influential friends. } }
   \line { \large { He's got very big connections and I follow his directions. } }
   \line { \large { Bernie knows his way around and so I always do what Bernie recommends. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { I am blessed with my attorney Bernie. I'm impressed with the way he runs the store. } }
   \line { \large { He's got Dodger season boxes and an office full of foxes. } }
   \line { \large { It's amazing all the different things your average guy might need a lawyer for. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { Bernie tells me what to do. Bernie lays it on the line. } }
   \line { \large { Bernie says, we sue, we sue. Bernie says, we sign, we sign. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { I'm in touch with my attorney Bernie. In a clutch he can speed right to the scene. } }
   \line { \large { And if I'm locked up in the jail with just one phone call for my bail } }
   \line { \large { he said to call his club collect or deal directly with his answering machine. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { And when I dine with my attorney Bernie, he buys wine from the rare imported rack. } }
   \line { \large { That's 'cause Bernie is a purist and not your polyester tourist. } }
   \line { \large { Bernie waves the glass around awhile, then takes a sip and always sends it back. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { Bernie tells me what to do. Bernie lays it on the line. } }
   \line { \large { Bernie says, we sue, we sue. Bernie says, we sign, we sign. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { I admire my attorney Bernie. I admire any guy who knows his stuff. } }
   \line { \large { Sure we blew a couple ventures with the counterfeit debentures, } }
   \line { \large { But you win a few, you lose a few. Like Bernie says, “You keep on hanging tough” } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { Thanks to you, my attorney Bernie, thanks to you I'm considered well to do. } }
   \line { \large { Sure I made out like a bandit just exactly like you planned it, } }
   \line { \large { but like Murray, my accountant told me yesterday, I owe it all to you. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { Bernie tells me what to do. Bernie lays it on the line. } }
   \line { \large { Bernie says, we sue, we sue. Bernie says, we sign, we sign. } }
   \vspace #1
   \line { \large { On the dotted line. } }
 }
